00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:47.000
AT THE UNIVERSITY OF CALIFORNIA,

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:48.000
AT IRVINE, ZOOLOGIST

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:51.000
NANCY BERLEY USES ELMER'S GLUE

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:52.000
