PEOPLE ARE OBSESSED

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:07.000
WITH LOOKS, BECAUSE LOOKS HAVE

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:10.000
MARKED HEALTH OF OTHERS.

00:05:10.000 --> 00:05:11.000
Reporter: AND GOOD LOOKS

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:12.000
USUALLY REQUIRE SYMMETRY, SAYS

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:14.000
BIOLOGIST RANDY THORNHILL.

00:05:14.000 --> 00:05:15.000
NEUTRAL EXPRESSION

00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:17.000
FOR THE CAMERA, PLEASE.

00:05:17.000 --> 00:05:18.000
Reporter: AT THE UNIVERSITY

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:18.000
