00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.000
MEASURES PEOPLE'S SYMMETRY.

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:21.000
GOOD.

00:05:21.000 --> 00:05:22.000
Reporter: HOW BALANCED

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:23.000
THEIR BODIES ARE.

00:05:23.000 --> 00:05:25.000
HE STARTED THIS RESEARCH AFTER

00:05:25.000 --> 00:05:26.000
DISCOVERING THAT INSECTS

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:27.000
WITH GOOD SYMMETRY ATTRACT MORE

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:29.000
MATES.

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:32.000
DOES IT WORK FOR PEOPLE, TOO?

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:33.000
THORNHILL'S COMPUTER DRAWS LINES

00:05:33.000 --> 00:05:34.000
THROUGH THE FACE THAT MEASURE

00:05:34.000 --> 00:05:35.000
SYMMETRY.

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:37.000
FACES WITH THE HIGHEST SYMMETRY

00:05:37.000 --> 00:05:38.000
HAVE LOW NUMBERS.

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:41.000
SURE ENOUGH, MOST PEOPLE JUDGE

00:05:41.000 --> 00:05:43.000
THOSE FACES AS MORE ATTRACTIVE.

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:45.000
YEP, HE WAS RATED AS ONE

00:05:45.000 --> 00:05:46.000
OF THE MOST ATTRACTIVE.

00:05:46.000 --> 00:05:47.000
THORNHILL HAS RUN THESE TESTS

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:49.000
IN OTHER COUNTRIES WITH OTHER

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:50.000
CULTURES.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.000
EVERYWHERE, PEOPLE REGARD

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.000
SYMMETRY AS MORE ATTRACTIVE.

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:54.000
AND ON QUESTIONNAIRES,

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:56.000
THE SYMMETRICAL MEN REPORT

00:05:56.000 --> 00:05:57.000
HAVING MORE SEX.

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:59.000
MORE SEX PARTNERS

00:05:59.000 --> 00:05:59.000
