00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:13.000
SCIENTISTS SAY IT RELATES

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:16.000
TO SURVIVAL OF THE SPECIES.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:17.000
WE HAVE AN INSTINCT DEEP

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:18.000
IN THE PRIMITIVE PART

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:20.000
OF OUR BRAINS, A REPTILIAN

00:06:20.000 --> 00:06:22.000
BRAIN, THEY CALL IT, THAT TELLS

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:24.000
US TO TRY HARD TO MAKE SURE

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.000
OUR GENES CARRY ON.

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:27.000
THE BEST WAY TO DO THAT IS

00:06:27.000 --> 00:06:29.000
TO PICK HEALTHY MATES AND,

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:30.000
APPARENTLY, GOOD LOOKS --

00:06:30.000 --> 00:06:32.000
CLEAR SKIN, BRIGHT EYES, OFTEN

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:34.000
PREDICT GOOD GENES.

