HIS RESEARCH TEAM HAS OBSERVED

00:30:26.000 --> 00:30:28.000
THOUSANDS OF COUPLES, FIRST

00:30:28.000 --> 00:30:30.000
HITCHING THEM UP TO ELECTRODES.

